<title>POLAND: Remak revises up 1996 net profit.</title>
<headline>Remak revises up 1996 net profit.</headline>
<dateline>WARSAW 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Preliminary Remak results for</p>
<p>the financial year ending December 31, 1996.</p>
<p>(Figures in millions of zlotys unless stated)</p>
<p>						   1996	 1995</p>
<p>    operating loss			   1.83 vs    4.37 profit</p>
<p>    pre-tax profit			   0.30 vs    4.40</p>
<p>    net profit				 0.10 vs    2.19</p>
<p>NOTE - Full company name is Remak SA. Earlier the company</p>
<p>said its net profit for 1996 was 0.05 zlotys.</p>
<p>    net sales				 75.50 vs  110.38</p>
<p>    costs of sales			  68.15 vs  109.02</p>
<p>    extraordinary loss		     0.01 vs    0.00</p>
<p>    income tax				 0.20 vs    2.21</p>
<p>    other taxes				 na  vs     na</p>
<p>    financial revenues		    53.09 vs    1.70</p>
<p>    financial costs			 51.18 vs    1.85</p>
<p>-- Warsaw Newsroom +48 22 653 9700</p>
